author: Ben Makuch, Jason Koebler
title: Man Who Planned to Bomb Hospital Amid Pandemic Dies in Incident With FBI
description: The pandemic caused the suspect to “accelerate” his plans to car-bomb a hospital, the agency said.
content: A domestic terrorism suspect in Belton, Missouri who allegedly planned to carbomb a hospital struggling with the coronavirus pandemic died while the FBI was trying to arrest him Tuesday, the agency confirmed. It is currently unclear whether FBI agents shot hi… [+2784 chars]
